         mean "any" as classes.

      - gwm now properly dies when the X server dies 
        (shown by qjb@athena.mit.edu). Was due to a bus error in a signal 
        handler...

      - problems in shaped windows decoration

    COMPATIBLE ENHANCEMENTS:

